# Sayar ‚Äî WhatsApp Checkout Platform (MVP)

**TL;DR:** For WhatsApp-first SMEs (starting with beauty/cosmetics), build a self‚Äëcheckout flow that turns inbound WhatsApp chats into paid orders ‚Äî with **native WhatsApp catalog browsing & cart**, address capture via **WhatsApp Flows** (with inline fallback), **simple discount codes at checkout**, and instant **payment links** ‚Äî so merchants close sales without manual replies.

---

## Users & Value

- **Primary user / persona:** Owner/manager of a Nigerian beauty brand (e.g., Amari) selling via WhatsApp DMs.
- **Secondary users:** Store staff/ops, Sayar admins (internal).

- **Jobs-to-be-done (JTBD):**
  - When a customer DMs ‚ÄúHi, price?‚Äù on WhatsApp, I want the chat to guide them to browse and pay by themselves, so I don‚Äôt lose sales to slow replies.
  - When customers return, I want their saved addresses to speed checkout, so repeat purchases are frictionless.
  - When an order is paid, I want automatic confirmation in the same chat and a clean dashboard view, so fulfillment is straightforward.
  - When a customer has a **discount code**, I want them to apply it easily during checkout so AOV and conversion improve without agent intervention.

